text: Ærest on easthealfe ys cinges land, & on suðhealfe burh stræt, & on westhealfe þæs hiredes land to Cristes Cyricean, & on norðhealfe se lictun.

Nu is þis þara twegra æcera gemæru, on easthealfe liþ þæs hiredes land inn to Cristes Cyricean, & on suðhealfe þæs abbates inn to apuldere, & on westhealfe portmanna land, & on norðhealfe cinges stræt.
Nu is eft þis þara oðra twegra æcera gemæru, on easthealfe liþ Æþestanes land, & on suþhealfe cincges stræt, & on westhealfe & on norðhealfe þæs hiredes land inn to Sancte Augustine.
Nu is þis ðæs anes æceres gemæru, on easthealfe liþ Æþestanes land, & on suðhealfe & on westhealfe cincges stræt, & on norðhealfe ðæs hirides inn to Sancte Augustine.
Nu is þis þæs syxtan æceres gemæru, on easthealfe lið cincges stræt, & on suðhealfe hryþera ceap, & on westhealfe Æþestanes land & on norðhealfe.
